            <abstract id="ref3" label="Abstract">This scrapbook details the career of the actress and singer Lillian Russell. Russell was one of the most popular performers of her era and became politically active during her later years. The scrapbook is composed mostly of newspaper clippings, but also includes correspondence, photographs, and other ephemera.</abstract>
        </did>
